  <brief_title>Six Months DHEA Treatment in Female Adrenal Failure</brief_title>
  <official_title>Physiolocal Effects of 6 Months DHEA Substitutional Therapy in Female Adrenal Failure in a Randomised, Placebo Controlled and Overcrossed Study.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>University of Aarhus</agency>
