  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Female,

          -  Adrenal insuficiency,

          -  Stable and safe anticonception,

          -  Stable hydrocortison substituation treatment.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Neoplastic and thromboembolic disease,

          -  Diabetes mellitus.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
